{"text": "13. DIVIDEND AND BONUS PAYMENTS", "bbox": [162.5, 1197.8, 558.4, 1218.7]}, {"text": "On November 10, 2005, in connection with the closing of the TD Group Loan Facility (see Note 9),", "bbox": [204.2, 1233.0, 1037.1, 1253.9]}, {"text": "TransDigm Inc. paid a cash dividend to TransDigm Holdings and made bonus payments to certain members of", "bbox": [162.5, 1258.0, 1087.9, 1278.9]}, {"text": "TransDigm’s management. The aggregate amount of the cash dividend and bonus payments made by TransDigm", "bbox": [162.5, 1283.0, 1107.4, 1303.9]}, {"text": "Inc. was approximately $104 million. TransDigm Holdings used all of the proceeds received by it from the", "bbox": [162.5, 1308.0, 1055.0, 1328.9]}, {"text": "payment of the cash dividend from TransDigm Inc. to pay a cash dividend to TD Group. On November 10, 2005,", "bbox": [162.5, 1333.0, 1108.3, 1353.9]}, {"text": "TD Group used the net proceeds received from the TD Group Loan Facility of approximately $193.8 million", "bbox": [162.5, 1358.0, 1070.2, 1378.9]}, {"text": "together with substantially all of the proceeds received from the dividend payment from TransDigm Holdings to", "bbox": [162.5, 1383.0, 1099.9, 1403.9]}, {"text": "(i) prepay the entire outstanding principal amount and all accrued and unpaid interest on its 12% senior", "bbox": [162.5, 1408.0, 1023.9, 1428.9]}, {"text": "unsecured promissory notes that were issued by it in connection with the Merger in July 2003, with all such", "bbox": [162.5, 1433.0, 1061.4, 1453.9]}, {"text": "F-20", "bbox": [617.8, 1483.4, 657.2, 1504.2]}]}